## Get your OAuth 1.0a credentials from https://developer.x.com/
## (App type: "Web App, Automated App or Bot" with 3-legged OAuth 1.0a enabled)
CONSUMER_KEY=your_consumer_key_here
CONSUMER_SECRET=your_consumer_secret_here
PORT=3000

## For production, set your domain callback URL:
## This must match the Callback URL configured in your X app.
# REDIRECT_URI=https://vibte.co/callback

## Access control token:
## Main page requires a valid token in the URL, e.g. https://vibte.co?token=lfghsfdbnlkvgdhsoiflgh
## Tokens are stored in db.json (LowDB). On first run a default token is seeded:
## lfghsfdbnlkvgdhsoiflgh
